    {
      "block_type": "title",
      "content": "二、问题分析",
      "page_num": 2,
      "section_path": [
        "论坛：www.openedv.com",
        "广州市星翼电子科技有限公司",
        "二、问题分析"
      ],
      "is_ocr": false,
      "raw_table": null
    },
    {
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "内核在初始化emmc 驱动的时候出现异常报错，emmc 不能正常初始化使用。",
      "page_num": 2,
      "section_path": [
        "论坛：www.openedv.com",
